00:58:57.480 --> 00:58:58.313
things a little bit.

00:59:06.040 --> 00:59:06.820
Again, apologies.

00:59:06.820 --> 00:59:07.737
I'm eating chalk here.

00:59:14.790 --> 00:59:16.440
So I'm going to
