00:59:40.160 --> 00:59:44.860
So I'm going to rearrange stuff
so that I can then write--

00:59:44.860 --> 00:59:45.760
just one moment.

00:59:54.990 --> 00:59:55.490
Oh.

01:00:00.750 --> 01:00:01.890
Apologies.

01:00:01.890 --> 01:00:05.162
This whole thing,
